Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:13.74,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Your sword is terrifyingly fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:16.23,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing, but do you really think
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:20.83,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll defeat me by the time\N the flames on that table strike 12?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:24.51,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you being rather conceited,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:26.08,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Mister...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:27.75,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:31.25,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:33.47,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Jean Pierre Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:35.77,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Merci beaucoup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:38.04,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:39.30,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:47.26,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Polnareff,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:49.37,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,don't assume that my flames
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:53.86,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,always burn upward or downwind \Nas they would in nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:58.49,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It is called Magician's Red\N because it controls flames freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:02.91,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,In the beginning, this world \Nwas engulfed in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:05.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect nothing less from Magician's Red,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:09.12,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who controls the flames that \Nsuggest the beginning of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:12.91,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,But, you say I'm being conceited?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:15.81,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that my swordsmanship
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:18.01,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is mere conceit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:22.85,JoJo-Foom,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Foom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:31.29,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,In the moment they lined up,\N he pierced five coins in a single strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:34.32,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,No. Take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:36.70,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:42.03,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see... there are flames between each coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:46.21,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you understand what this means.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:48.19,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It is not conceit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:52.92,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,My Stand has the power to sever even fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:58.89,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It can slash the very air and create gaps \Nbetween nothingness and nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:06.10,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Which means your Magician's Red is \Npowerless before my Silver Chariot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:13.65,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,When did he...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:16.08,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,The card that my Stand has,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:19.91,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chariot, suggests conquest and victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:23.58,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind taking care of you \Nin this cramped little space,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:26.51,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,but, Avdol, you'd be able to use your
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:29.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,flame abilities in a much more open space, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:33.66,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It would be fitting for my Stand to \Ndefeat you under those circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:35.01,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,A fitting victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:40.92,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:57.48,JoJo-MainTitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,1)}JoJo's {\c&H2E0FB2&}Bizarre Adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:57.48,JoJo-MainTitle2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,1)}Stardust Crusaders
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:15.09,JoJo-EpTitle,epi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,461)}Episode 5: Silver Chariot
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.09,JoJo-top,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:21.64,JoJo-Location,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,459)\b0\fs18}This story is fiction. The characters, groups, places, laws, and names \Nused in this program have no connection to any existing in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:18.21,JoJo-top,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tiger Balm Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.02,JoJo-top,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:21.78,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger Balm Garden,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:27.07,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,a garden that exists along the hillside \Nof Hong Kong's Tai Hang Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:29.43,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Its unique taste and appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:32.20,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,make it number one among \NHong Kong's bizarre zones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:35.27,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I will make a prediction here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:37.42,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,First, Avdol,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:43.17,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,you will be destroyed by \Nyour own Stand's powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.28,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Avdol...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.18,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro, you need not interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:51.56,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,With such an open space,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:55.11,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can control my Stand as freely as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.37,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:09.36,JoJo-Slice,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Slice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:16.00,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.00,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.84,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to use your precious \Nflames to your heart's content?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:23.55,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,If not, I'm going to take my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:27.30,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:41.07,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard. He's mocking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:45.07,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,With repeated stabs, he carved a\N statue that looks just Magician's Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.34,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:52.58,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You fit quite well in this garden, Magician's Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:58.33,JoJo-Bam2,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(608,1)}Suuuuuck
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.35,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.89,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're ready to show your true power?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:04.01,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.34,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take what you dish out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.27,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hide behind something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:08.95,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Avdol is going to use {\i1}it{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:10.05,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,"It"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:17.10,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Crossfire Hurricane!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.24,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you've got?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:25.28,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that my swordsmanship can create gaps
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:28.32,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,between nothingness and nothingness, \Nand blow away flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.28,JoJo-Bam2,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Crash
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:37.54,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Avdol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:41.79,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The flames are so strong\N that he's being burned, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:48.26,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as I predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:51.54,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You will die, burned by your own flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:57.02,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good, good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.83,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going to come at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:06:59.81,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,How unsightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.69,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What is this odd resistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:06.65,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:07.90,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:11.28,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,How can flames come out \Nfrom the body I severed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.85,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:16.15,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's the statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.76,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes were blinded by the flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:25.59,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,What you cut apart was the statue\N that Silver Chariot carved earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:29.13,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that I could control my flames freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.11,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,The flames that you blew back toward it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:35.18,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,melted its joints and caused it to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:39.51,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,You are the one defeated \Nby his own Stand's powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:42.94,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,And now, face this again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.81,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Crossfire Hurricane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:53.20,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's ten years too \Nsoon for you to fight me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:56.20,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,a fortune teller, with predictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.54,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Such terrifying power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:05.04,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Since his Stand took that head-on,\N it must have melted. It's done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:07.05,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,That's one hell of a burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.93,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's dead. If he's lucky, \Nhe'll be in serious condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:12.24,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that'd be bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:15.97,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, he won't be\N able to stand for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:18.67,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,His Stand is destroyed and unable to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:21.18,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Mr. Joestar,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:23.75,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,let us hurry on our journey to Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.84,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:29.36,JoJo-Boom,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Boom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.80,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:37.32,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,His Stand is breaking into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.08,JoJo-Bam2,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(417,1)}Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:43.16,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,He flew into the air while still lying down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:47.17,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo! Oh, bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:48.67,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.12,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.83,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,He's perfectly fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:54.80,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,But why is his body floating in the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.72,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look with your inner eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:00.14,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:08.61,JoJo-Bang,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(610,1)}Bam
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.17,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:08.61,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,My Stand with its armor off: Silver Chariot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.91,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You seem shocked,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:14.53,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and it wouldn't be honorable to defeat you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.80,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,without explaining my powers first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:20.16,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You could even call it a surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:24.33,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Would you give me the time to explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:27.27,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:29.11,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear this explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:34.42,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,My Stand did not break apart and disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:40.15,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Chariot was wearing armor.\N That's what it just took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:43.04,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What was burned away by your \Nflames was just part of its armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.52,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was only lightly injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:49.26,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,And with its armor off, it is lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:52.52,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see it lift me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:56.78,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That's how fast it can move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:58.58,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:01.67,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that because \Nits armor was so heavy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:05.46,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,it had to take my Crossfire Hurricane head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:10.55,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,But that would also mean that it's naked now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.30,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it doesn't have its protection,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:16.42,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,if it were to take that attack\N again, it wouldn't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:22.41,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Oui, precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.52,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,But that would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:29.19,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible? I'd like to test that theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:33.19,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm going to show \Nyou something astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:35.44,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:38.28,JoJo-Bam3,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Line-up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:38.28,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:42.70,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,His Stand just multiplied into six... \Nno, now there are seven of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.49,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:46.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,There should only be one Stand to each user.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.54,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you are astonished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.32,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,These are shadow clones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:58.01,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow clones of my Stand that confuse \Nnot only your eyes, but your senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:02.01,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Your senses can't follow its movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:06.56,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like its swordsmanship now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:15.98,JoJo-Eyecatch3,sign top,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}Silver Chariot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:15.98,JoJo-Eyecatch2,sign bot,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1047,0)}Jean Pierre Polnareff
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:23.20,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Red Bind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:37.05,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that you wouldn't be\N able to follow its movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:40.13,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Your flames can only grasp shadow clones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:48.09,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Striking at random now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:51.27,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting a bit desperate, Avdol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.15,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's true; that'll just use up all his energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:12:01.15,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Crossfire Hurricane!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.51,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Non, non, non, non, non, non.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.99,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,That is also a shadow clone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:13.21,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Your attack will not work against my Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:14.79,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.08,JoJo-main,some,0000,0000,0000,,Avdol!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:23.59,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Such precision. Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.95,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,a Stand ability that has\N been very highly trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:30.35,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,For certain reasons,\N I trained for nearly ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:33.28,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come at me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:36.19,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I will finish you with my next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:41.29,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of chivalry,\N you keep explaining your attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:43.11,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,You're rather honorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:45.46,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I shall also
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:48.33,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,reveal a secret before beginning my next attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:51.16,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:55.68,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,You see, there are variations \Nto my Crossfire Hurricane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:58.92,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It is a flame in the shape of an Ankh, \Nbut it need not be singular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:02.42,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I can break it up and make it fly in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:07.95,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Crossfire Hurricane
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.47,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Special!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.48,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Just try and dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.19,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You waste your time, Avdol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:21.61,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,They formed a circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.69,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,There's no opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:25.15,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Naïve! Naïve, naïve, naïve, naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.45,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You're naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:31.20,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I will again use this power against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:35.59,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Sever! Blow it back at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:38.79,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:40.56,JoJo-Grab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kaboom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.76,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:52.43,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The hole that was made by the flames earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.72,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:56.81,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The first flames were used to dig a tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:14:00.06,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,And then he shot the Crossfire Hurricane through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.31,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.11,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can break apart my flames
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:05.32,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and make them fly in as many pieces as I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:16.75,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Burning is a rather painful way to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.08,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Use that dagger to kill yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.02,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I was conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:40.41,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't imagine his flames
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:42.46,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,standing a chance against my swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:47.48,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a good sport and burn to death after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:53.16,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was defeated by your powers, \Nit is only due courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:56.69,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It would be disrespectful to kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:06.26,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, you remember to be chivalrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:10.78,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,And you did not throw your \Ndagger when I had my back turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:15.60,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Despite having orders from DIO, \Nyour proud honor shines through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.16,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a shame to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:21.69,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a reason behind his actions...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.65,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Jojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:24.57,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:31.16,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh. Those tentacles are so gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:33.86,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro, hurry up and get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:35.41,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:35.41,JoJo-overlap,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.68,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Now that the flesh bud is gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:44.28,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we can be {\i1}bud{\i0}dies. Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:49.40,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin, don't guys like him \Nwho make stupid puns
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:51.52,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,seriously piss you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:57.81,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The boat that we had chartered \Nfrom the Speedwagon crew
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:00.31,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,yesterday should be at the harbor now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:04.69,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Is there \Nsomething else you needed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:06.71,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:10.57,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't thanked you for\N freeing me from DIO's spell yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:13.24,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,For that, you need to thank Jojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.02,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:19.29,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It appears there's no one \Nto accept your kind thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:24.73,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I don't like to be pushy, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.84,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,But there is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:32.22,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Joestar, I'd like to ask \Nyou a very bizarre question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.22,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,A bizarre question?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:36.64,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive my curiosity,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:39.43,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but even while eating, \Nyou didn't take off your gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:43.48,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Your left arm wouldn't happen \Nto be a right arm, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:46.56,JoJo-main,joeaph,0000,0000,0000,,What? My left arm, a right arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:49.07,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That is indeed a bizarre question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.57,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:56.20,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the man\N who killed my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:59.30,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:03.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But he has two right arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:13.59,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I lost it in a battle fifty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:18.10,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for my rudeness. Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:21.85,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, tell us what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:30.36,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three years now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:38.12,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,My younger sister was walking home from school
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.68,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with a classmate one rainy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:43.54,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It was a country road in my native France.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:46.24,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,On the side of the road, a man stood
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.97,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with his back to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:51.90,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Mysteriously, even though it was raining,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.17,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the rain fell around him in a dome-like shape,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.87,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,as if an invisible screen surrounded him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:18:01.06,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, as if cut down by a scythe,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:03.18,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,her classmate's chest was sliced open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.01,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:18.89,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,My sister was shamed and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:22.51,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,That was all that man wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:27.66,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Barely escaping death,\N her friend somehow survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:31.16,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she didn't see his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:33.49,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but both of his arms were right arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:40.59,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,No one believed her testimony, \Nbut I understood it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:44.39,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Because I believed that man\N may have a similar power to the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.85,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,one that I had been keeping a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.60,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely a Stand user.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:50.77,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I swore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:54.59,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's soul would not be able
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:57.88,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to rest unless he atoned with his death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:19:01.49,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I will use my Stand for retribution!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:06.45,JoJo-Menacing,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Menacing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:05.53,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Then, a year ago, I met DIO.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.09,JoJo-Foom2,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(168,1)}Blam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:27.98,JoJo-flashback,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I see s-something in the crystal ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:29.48,JoJo-flashback,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:33.18,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,A vision. I didn't create it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:38.49,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,What's inside your heart is \Nbeing projected via my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.57,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:44.61,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to be friends with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:51.55,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Something is bothering you. You're in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:56.50,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Stick with me,\Nand it'll disappear from your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:20:00.49,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,What's being shown in the \Ncrystal is what pains you, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:03.01,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:05.82,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,I have pain of my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:09.17,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,My body cannot go out into the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:11.95,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,So please, help me, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:15.01,JoJo-flashback,dio,0000,0000,0000,,I shall find this man for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:24.47,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,And then I was ordered to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.86,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I believed that was the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:30.95,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It's partially because of the flesh bud,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:34.95,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but DIO's also skilled at manipulating others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:38.21,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. But according to what you just said,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:41.48,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,it would appear that DIO has\N found the man with two right arms
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:42.93,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and has joined forces with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:47.14,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to go to Egypt with all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.44,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,If I go after DIO,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:50.81,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to find the \None who took my sister's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:53.26,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:55.89,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I have no objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:59.98,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'd follow us, even if we said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:02.54,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Jean Pierre Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:08.69,JoJo-Names4,sign bot,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(169,1)}Jean Pierre Polnareff
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:05.44,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Stand name: Silver Chariot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:08.69,JoJo-Names6,sign top,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(387,1)}Silver Chariot
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:08.70,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Powers: Fast and precise swordsmanship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:11.11,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:13.85,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Good grie—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.55,JoJo-overlap,girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:18.50,JoJo-main,girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind taking our picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:19.60,JoJo-internal/narrator,girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,He's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:21.46,JoJo-internal/narrator,girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use this as my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:23.43,JoJo-main,girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:25.60,JoJo-main,girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,We want our backs toward the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:27.80,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying me! Ask someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:29.75,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:31.97,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take your picture for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:33.18,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Come, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:36.94,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You have very nice legs. \NLet's get a full body shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.37,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:42.86,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.69,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Très bien!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:45.98,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the button,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:49.53,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to push, push, push \Nyour hearts toward mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:53.20,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I don't quite understand his personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:55.46,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,That was a very sudden change of mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:22:00.46,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,More like his head and his lower \Nhalf are very clearly separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:04.48,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:37.02,JoJo-Preview,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:38.64,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do something about that uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:40.87,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Students should act like students.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:43.15,JoJo-main,kid,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on! I'll take you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:44.74,JoJo-main,some,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a Stand user?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:48.74,JoJo-main,some,0000,0000,0000,,If a Stand user inhales any cigarette smoke at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:50.03,JoJo-NextTitle,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 6:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:50.03,JoJo-NextTitle2,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Blue Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:50.03,JoJo-main,some,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
